data.description: Experience this stunning home nestled in the bourgeoning Downtown Pompano. Smart floor plan designed for modern living, this home boasts a spacious living and dining area that offers ample room for relaxation and entertainment. Beautiful new porcelain floors throughout the living space and ceramic floors in all bedrooms. Spacious closets, and linen closet next to the bathroom. The Kitchen has plenty of natural light and a pantry with a countertop dishwasher included.  Brand new washer/dryer. Large Lot 7,000 sq. ft. with spacious side yards.  Accordion shutters throughout the home, storage space, an attached carport for your vehicle, and ample parking spaces for guests
